  "detailed_description": "<h1>join us</h1><p>Players who want to experience this game first can contact us through the group at any time, and we will provide you with a serial number. We hope you can let more players see this game through live broadcast!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/4611d20501326054ec10177bbaa37e9a.webp?t=1762982870\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Hundreds of monsters are attacking you on the same screen, and you can only face it alone. The rich monsters will bring you the most exciting experience!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/825a907463e820d8c4b1de6d0f4fead8.poster.avif?t=1762982870\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/825a907463e820d8c4b1de6d0f4fead8.webm?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/825a907463e820d8c4b1de6d0f4fead8.mp4?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/2488955854a73fa0034eb3e96a2b6774.webp?t=1762982870\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Different bosses have different attack skills, super fast movement speed, wall of beasts coming towards you, and position-locked sprint attacks. The attacks of each boss will be your nightmare!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/ae5ba08861bbdb32c2b6470c2242a968.poster.avif?t=1762982870\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/ae5ba08861bbdb32c2b6470c2242a968.webm?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/ae5ba08861bbdb32c2b6470c2242a968.mp4?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/a0a4b64cd13097abc2ab0543a3cb70ac.webp?t=1762982870\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>You decide the upgrade route, which contains more than 20 props, and each prop has more than ten branch upgrade routes. Different routes determine different gameplay. No matter what choice you make, it will lead to victory!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/08f818036e1d427e257758bc6791c71d.poster.avif?t=1762982870\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/08f818036e1d427e257758bc6791c71d.webm?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/08f818036e1d427e257758bc6791c71d.mp4?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/e1116f8ac9eb584b5dd4a8706d9e06bc.webp?t=1762982870\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Is it a summoning stream, a buff burst, or a large area of ​​high attack value crushing. Different genres have different gameplays. It all depends on your preference whether you want to move coquettishly or do violent output!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/77c8c1b941f8f09e2fbe3784d0212201.poster.avif?t=1762982870\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/77c8c1b941f8f09e2fbe3784d0212201.webm?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/77c8c1b941f8f09e2fbe3784d0212201.mp4?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/255992c3bbd2d3b77dfc25b7e529cc15.webp?t=1762982870\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Is it a steel rider? Yue Yuan? Or the lonely-eyed swordsman? Each character has its own exclusive skills! A super long flying sword attack, a delayed explosive bomb, or a broken sword that kills at close range, your choice will determine your start!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/060f77cd03bb36f858a3f015f1f065c5.poster.avif?t=1762982870\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/060f77cd03bb36f858a3f015f1f065c5.webm?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/060f77cd03bb36f858a3f015f1f065c5.mp4?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/d25dd09345865dc710f4a1ecbe09ef6c.webp?t=1762982870\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Earn gold coins, continuously upgrade your talents, and with the blessing of buffs, you can kill ruthlessly and become unstoppable! The moment you start the game, victory is declared!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/467fa1c9a72a0595961e22f1cad12fb1.poster.avif?t=1762982870\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/467fa1c9a72a0595961e22f1cad12fb1.webm?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491050/extras/467fa1c9a72a0595961e22f1cad12fb1.mp4?t=1762982870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
